entor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Line-Following Robot<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c4a9562 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c4a9562\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f0454bd e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f0454bd\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6cab5cf elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"6cab5cf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Line_following_robot-1024x683.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1726\" alt=\"line following robot\" srcset=\"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Line_following_robot-1024x683.png 1024w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Line_following_robot-300x200.png 300w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Line_following_robot-768x512.png 768w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Line_following_robot.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"  title=\"Line-Following Robot\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e43db40 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e43db40\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7007a98 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"7007a98\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"576\" height=\"1024\" src=\"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Line_following_robot_on_map-576x1024.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1727\" alt=\"line following robot on map\" srcset=\"http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Line_following_robot_on_map-576x1024.jpg 576w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Line_following_robot_on_map-169x300.jpg 169w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Line_following_robot_on_map-768x1365.jpg 768w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Line_following_robot_on_map-864x1536.jpg 864w, http:\/\/my-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Line_following_robot_on_map.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px\"  title=\"Line-Following Robot\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-16551a2 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"16551a2\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aec1cb3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"aec1cb3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The objective of this project was to design and optimise an autonomous line-following robot capable of navigating a track quickly and reliably.<\/p><p>Starting from a standard Arduino-based robot kit, we progressively improved both the software and the robot&#8217;s behaviour by implementing a PID controller, handling sharp turns independently, integrating obstacle detection and developing a system for wireless parameter tuning.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9cb5248 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"9cb5248\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6e92ab7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6e92ab7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Project Information<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6d7446a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"6d7446a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-75b8ba8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"75b8ba8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Duration<\/strong><\/p><p>October &#8211; December 2025<\/p><p><strong>Team<\/strong><\/p><p>3 students<\/p><p><strong>Technologies<\/strong><\/p><p>Arduino \u2022 C++ \u2022 PID Control \u2022 Infrared Sensors \u2022 Ultrasonic Sensor<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aaf655b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"aaf655b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Development Process<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d617e05 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d617e05\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The project followed an iterative approach where we continuously tested the robot, analysed its behaviour and refined the control algorithm.<\/p><p>Our first solution relied on a rule-based decision table that adjusted the speed of each wheel according to the infrared sensor readings. While functional, this approach quickly became difficult to maintain and produced abrupt movements.<\/p><p>To improve the robot&#8217;s performance, we replaced this logic with a PID controller that continuously adjusted the steering correction, resulting in smoother trajectories and more stable line tracking.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-34f4932 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"34f4932\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Key Features<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-71e097a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"71e097a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>PID Line Following<\/strong><\/p><p>Implemented a PID controller to continuously adjust the wheel speeds, improving stability and reducing oscillations on straight sections and curves.<\/p><p><strong>Sharp Turn Handling<\/strong><\/p><p>Added dedicated behaviours for very tight corners that could not be handled reliably by the PID controller alone.<\/p><p><strong>Wireless PID Tuning<\/strong><\/p><p>Developed a system allowing PID parameters to be modified remotely using a controller, making the tuning process significantly faster during testing.<\/p><p><strong>Obstacle Detection<\/strong><\/p><p>Integrated an ultrasonic sensor to stop the robot safely when obstacles were detected on the track.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aa329b2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"aa329b2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Testing &amp; Optimisation<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7a32912 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7a32912\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A large part of the project consisted of repeated testing and parameter tuning.<\/p><p>Different combinations of PID gains were evaluated to balance responsiveness, stability and cornering performance. We also adjusted the turning behaviour and speed profiles to improve overall lap consistency.<\/p><p>This iterative process highlighted the importance of testing control algorithms on real hardware, where small parameter changes could significantly affect the robot&#8217;s behaviour.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-79a58bf elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"79a58bf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Results<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-df69b1f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"df69b1f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The final robot successfully demonstrated:<\/p><p>\u2714 Smooth line following using PID control<\/p><p>\u2714 Stable cornering<\/p><p>\u2714 Wireless PID tuning<\/p><p>\u2714 Integrated obstacle detection<\/p><p>\u2714 Reliable autonomous navigation<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ae0123a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ae0123a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What I Learned<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-22fe18e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"22fe18e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>This project introduced me to feedback control and showed how iterative testing is essential when developing autonomous robots. By comparing a rule-based controller with a PID controller, I gained a practical understanding of how closed-loop control improves both stability and overall performance.<\/p><p>It also reinforced the importance of experimentation and parameter tuning when working with real robotic systems.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u2190 Back to Robotics Projects Line-Following Robot 